Filippa.

357
00:21:57,708 --> 00:21:58,608
Tissaia.

358
00:21:59,875 --> 00:22:00,958
Vilgefortz.

359
00:22:02,666 --> 00:22:04,541
Y Yennefer de Vengerberg.

